:root{--gallery-gap:clamp(8px,2.6vw,14px);--row-height:clamp(5px,1.2vw,6px);--arrow-bg:hsla(0,0%,100%,.95);--arrow-color:#111;--arrow-size:clamp(44px,9vw,46px)}.gallery-carousel{position:relative}.carousel-header{align-items:center;display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:flex-end;margin:12px 0 10px}.controls{display:flex;gap:8px}.nav-btn{background:var(--arrow-bg);border:0;border-radius:999px;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.18);color:var(--arrow-color);cursor:pointer;display:grid;height:var(--arrow-size);place-items:center;transition:transform .15s ease,background .15s ease,opacity .15s ease;width:var(--arrow-size)}.nav-btn:hover{background:#fff;transform:translateY(-1px)}.nav-btn:disabled{cursor:not-allowed;opacity:.4}.carousel-track{display:flex;overflow-x:auto;scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;scrollbar-width:none}.carousel-track::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}.slide{flex:0 0 100%;padding:4px 0;scroll-snap-align:start}.dots{display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;margin-top:10px;padding-bottom:calc(env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0px) + 4px)}.dot{background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);border:none;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;height:8px;transition:transform .15s ease,background .15s ease;width:8px}.dot.active{background:rgba(0,0,0,.6);transform:scale(1.1)}.masonry-grid{display:grid;gap:var(--gallery-gap);grid-auto-rows:var(--row-height);grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:0 2px}@media (min-width:380px){.masonry-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}@media (min-width:900px){.masonry-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}@media (max-width:640px){.carousel-header{-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(4px);backdrop-filter:blur(4px);background:hsla(0,0%,100%,.88);border-radius:999px;bottom:calc(env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0px) + var(--gallery-gap) + 28px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.15);margin:0;padding:6px;position:absolute;right:calc(var(--gallery-gap) + 2px);z-index:5}}.gallery-link{color:inherit;display:block;text-decoration:none;width:100%}.gallery-image{background:#0e0e0e;border-radius:12px;height:100%;margin:0;overflow:hidden;padding:0;position:relative}.gallery-image img{display:block;height:100%;-o-object-fit:cover;object-fit:cover;-o-object-position:center;object-position:center;width:100%}.gallery-image:after,.gallery-image:before{border:12px solid rgba(0,0,0,.1);content:"";inset:0;pointer-events:none;position:absolute;transition:all .2s;will-change:border}.gallery-image:after{border-width:0}.gallery-image figcaption{box-sizing:border-box;color:hsla(0,0%,100%,0);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;left:50%;line-height:1.25;max-width:calc(100% - 8em);padding:.9em;position:absolute;text-align:center;top:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);transition:all .2s ease;z-index:1}.gallery-image figcaption:after,.gallery-image figcaption:before{background:rgba(0,0,0,.18);bottom:100%;content:"";height:100%;opacity:0;padding:.9em;position:absolute;right:100%;transition:all .3s ease-in-out;width:100%;z-index:-1}.gallery-image figcaption:after{left:100%;top:100%}html:not(.touch) .gallery-image:hover:before{border-width:12px}html:not(.touch) .gallery-image:hover:after{border-width:24px}html:not(.touch) .gallery-image:hover figcaption{color:#fff;text-shadow:0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,.2);transition:all .2s ease .25s}html:not(.touch) .gallery-image:hover figcaption:after,html:not(.touch) .gallery-image:hover figcaption:before{opacity:1}html:not(.touch) .gallery-image:hover figcaption:before{bottom:-1.2em;right:-1.2em}html:not(.touch) .gallery-image:hover figcaption:after{left:-1.2em;top:-1.2em}html.touch .gallery-image figcaption{bottom:1.5em;color:#fff;left:50%;text-shadow:0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,.2);top:auto;transform:translateX(-50%)}html.touch .gallery-image figcaption:after,html.touch .gallery-image figcaption:before{bottom:-1.2em;opacity:1;right:-1.2em}html.touch .gallery-image figcaption:after{left:-1.2em;top:-1.2em}.goverlay{-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(2px);backdrop-filter:blur(2px);background:rgba(10,10,12,.92)}.glightbox-container .gbtn{background:hsla(0,0%,100%,.9);border-radius:999px;box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.25);color:#111;height:42px;transition:transform .15s ease,background .15s ease;width:42px}.glightbox-container .gbtn:hover{background:#fff;transform:translateY(-1px)}.glightbox-clean .gdesc-inner{color:#fff;font-size:14px;font-weight:600}@media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.dot,.gallery-image figcaption,.gallery-image figcaption:after,.gallery-image figcaption:before,.gallery-image:after,.gallery-image:before,.nav-btn{transition:none!important}}
